title: Surati Farsan Mart
typeOfFood: Lacto, Indian, Fast food, Take-out, Catering
description: An Indian sweets and snacks shop that also serves vegetarian Indian snack foods. Food menu includes masala dosa, samosa, petish (fried balls with stuffing), panipuri (small fried whole wheat puffy shells stuffed with spiced beans and potatoes), deli smabhar, and many more snack foods. Offers shipping via UPS. Modern interior featuring a glass snacks counter where you can see all the various sweets and snacks for sale by weight. Contemporary style furniture seating. Note that some things contain cheese, yogurt, or milk.
